 \u00e5 programmere den. Men det var en gave, sier hun. Med splitternytt web-kamera kan kompisene i Sverige f\u00e5 bildekontakt med Erik (5) og Sara (9) n\u00e5r de chatter. {ndash} Vi kj\u00f8per bare ting vi greier \u00e5 bruke, sier Johan L\u00e5ng og Solveig Sletvold."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "0563e36fc09dd5b81927dfae322b7863a4a3914c07addc972d9a183565a0eb95"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-03-09T22:24:03.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Spesielt digitale f\u00f8ler deg seg ikke. - Vi har ikke selvtenkende kj\u00f8leskap eller komfyr."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://static.polarismedia.no/skins/prod/publication/adressa/gfx/applefavicon.png"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/ae2e5ce69d0737a608f833a5e748ebc04e40667d.jpg?593b1cde"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "- Kj\u00f8per bare ting vi kan bruke -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "ae2e5ce69d0737a608f833a5e748ebc04e40667d"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "technology-and-computing"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["digital", "ting", "kj\u00f8pe"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["erik", "johan l\u00e5ng og solveig sletvold", "playstation ii"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["sara", "sverige"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["solveig sletvold", "johan l\u00e5ng"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://static.polarismedia.no/skins/prod/publication/adressa/gfx/applef